{#- Site footer — ported from production index.html (fetched from
    sergeselenko/everlane-realty-site@main, 2026-07-07), extended to the plan §2
    IA. Headings use h2 (styled small) — kills the audit §2.5 h3-skip defect. -#}
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="footer-brand__name">Everlane Realty</div>
        <div class="footer-brand__agent">{{ site.broker.name }}, {{ site.broker.title }}</div>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">
          {{ site.broker.street }}<br>
          {{ site.broker.city }}, {{ site.broker.state }} {{ site.broker.zip }}<br>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.broker.email }}">{{ site.broker.email }}</a><br>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.broker.phoneHref }}">{{ site.broker.phone }}</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <h2 class="footer-h">Explore</h2>
        <ul>
          {%- for item in nav.footerExplore %}
          <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a></li>
          {%- endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <h2 class="footer-h">The fine print</h2>
        <ul>
          {%- for item in nav.footerFinePrint %}
          <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a></li>
          {%- endfor %}
          <li>{{ site.mlsAttribution }}</li>
          <li>License #{{ site.broker.license }}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__legal">
      <p class="fairhousing"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" role="img" aria-label="Equal Housing Opportunity logo" focusable="false" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:7px;fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:1.5"><path d="M3.5 11 L12 4 L20.5 11"/><path d="M5.5 9.7 V20 H18.5 V9.7"/><line x1="9" y1="13" x2="15" y2="13"/><line x1="9" y1="16" x2="15" y2="16"/></svg>Equal Housing Opportunity. All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. We are committed to the letter and spirit of U.S. fair housing law.</p>
      {#- Studio one-liner slot (plan §2 #8 + §4a loudness DEFAULT: footer line + /ai colophon). Studio NAME is a placeholder pending the operator's naming reconcile (plan §11.5). #}
      <p class="footer__studio">This site runs on Everlane&rsquo;s own studio automation <span class="stub-note" title="studio name placeholder — operator naming reconcile pending (plan §11.5)">[studio-name TODO]</span> &mdash; data refreshes itself; every client-facing decision is the broker&rsquo;s. <a href="/ai/">See how this site runs &rarr;</a></p>
      <p>&copy; <span data-year>2026</span> Everlane Realty. {{ site.broker.name }}, {{ site.broker.title }}. Brokerage identification per FREC 61J2&#8209;10.025. MLS listing content is provided by IDX Broker and the participating MLS, and is the property of the MLS.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
